clush-svc tries to simplify system services management in Linux clusters. It
uses ClusterShell's API and mimicks clush.
Planned features:
 * start/stop/restart/status of any service across cluster nodes
 * definition of services groups and dependances
 * GUI

Authors: Franck Nguyen, Alexandre Sicard
This project is part of our Cluster and Grid Computing class with Patrice Lucas
at Université d'Évry.
